blog.title: phanfiction catalogue
blog.description:
mobile users, click here!

please refer to our FAQ first.

Our goal is to create an alphabetized library of every phanfiction in the phandom. Besides that, we compile masterlists of different genres that are scheduled for posting every few days, and help find fics that have been mislocated.

summary: Coming Out To Each Other Masterlist
title: Coming Out To Each Other Masterlist
body:
All You Did Will Be Undone (ao3) - INeverHadMyInternetPhase

Summary: What 2009 phan would have looked like if they were ace and wanted to be in a QPR.

And Love is Not a Choice - darren-fucking-chriss

Summary: It’s 2009 and Dan realises he still hasn’t told Phil he’s bisexual and not straight.

A New Point Of View (fanfiction.net) - ImagineIfItWere.Real 

Summary: Dan comes out to Phil as bi, and Phil comes out to Dan as gay, and awkward/sexy flirting ensues.

Colour Me Free (ao3) - orphan_account

Summary: At age 25, Dan Howell doesn’t want to hide anymore. The problem is, it’s not exactly easy to tell your boyfriend of 7 years that you’re not a girl.

Coming Out - hannah-lucyy

Summary: Teen Dan and Phil are inseparable friends who tell each other everything, but there’s still one thing Phil needs to say. And to put it simply … he’s terrified to do so.

Coming Out (fanfiction.net) - CheekyButterfly 

Summary: Phil loves Dan, but doesn’t want to scare Dan away. But what if Dan feels the exact same way?

Here Goes Nothing (ao3) - iihappydaysii

Summary: This is something Phil has been struggling with for awhile and he’s finally ready to tell Dan.

Let The Salt Dry - dandrogynous

Summary: “When I look at my old pictures, all I can see is what I used to be but am no longer. I think: What I can see is what I am not.” - Aleksandar Hemona (2009 except Dan is a trans boy)

Losing A Piece Of Me - huphilpuffs

Summary: Sometimes Dan likes boys more than he likes girls, and gets upset with himself for it.

Love Songs For Robots - dantiloquent

Summary: Phil is aromantic and asexual, and Dan doesn’t know exactly what that means to start with, but he learns, and it’s okay, they’re okay, of course they’re okay. because asexuality and aromanticism isn’t always grief and loneliness.

Regrets Almost Made - nightowlhowell

Summary: Dan ends up coming out to Phil not in the way he would have preferred.

Sundresses And Plaid Shirts - crescendohowell

Summary: Dan comes to terms with being genderfluid and meets a very supportive Phil.

body:
June 4: In Any World (Chapter Three)

Explicit

Tags: Alternative Universes, universe hopping, friends to lovers, fanfiction, getting together

Summary:  Returning home after his second world tour, Dan feels lost, bored, and without direction. But things are about to get much more exciting when, while reading fanfiction in the bath,  Dan slips, hits his head, and passes out. When he wakes up, it’s to a world that definitely isn’t the one he came from, especially because his best friend is in bed with him. And if he thinks that is strange, things are about to get a whole lot weirder.

Tags for this chapter:  somnophilia, reincarnation (ok, kind of), Sex toys

Start from the beginning ¦ Read on ao3
